India’s First Pomedy Show (Poetry + Comedy) | Manhar Seth, Badal Sharma, Rajat Sood

Presenting the first-ever Pomedy Show of India – GOSSIP BOYS!
A unique blend of poetry, comedy, and real talk, where we laugh at the things we once cried over.

From heartbreaks to hustle, awkward texts to late-night feelings — nothing is off-limits.

latestPosts.caption:
Baarish mein bheetgi hui ek shyaam mein apne kamre leta hua main Diwar pe latki hui ghadi ki suiyo ko dekh raha hu,
Aur mujhe tumhaari yaad aa rahi hai.
Ye suiyan mujhe hamaari yaad dilaati hai.
Jaise woh minute waala main, 
Aur woh second waali tum.
Poore din ek dusre ke peeche bhaagte rehte,
Kabhi tum hamaare pass aane ki koshish karti toh kabhi ham.
Bhaagam daudi ka ye silsila poore din chalta hi rehta tha.
Bar beech mein kabhi kabhi thak ke, 
Tum hampar aaram karti thi. 
Ceene pe sar rakh ke so jaati thi.
Zyaada der ke liye nahi,
Par agli baar tak sukoon dene ke liye kaafi.
Shayad isiliye jab bhi 12 bajte the toh mere armaano ke bhi 12 bajte the

Hamara ishq ghadi jaisa nahi tha.
Hamara ishq waqt jaisa tha.
Kyunki ghadi toh ruk sakti hai.
Par waqt nahi rukta.
Aur mujhe bhi nahi rukna tha.
Par shayad tumhe aage nahi badna tha.
Aur mainn ye baat bhool jaata hu ki ek ghadi tab tak hi sahi rehti hai jab tak suiyan ek disha mein aage bade.
Toh agar ghadi hamara rishta tha aur suiyan hum the, 
Toh tumne boht pehle hi saath chalna chorh diya tha.

Tu ghadi thi main tujhe rok nahi paya
Main woh waqt tha jo tu rakh nahi paayi

Par poori zindigi main sirf ye baat nahi samajh paaya.
Ki main agar minute tha aur tum second,
Toh ishq toh ghanta hi hona tha na.
